                    <span>Aldo Leopold summarizes many environmental movements within this compilation of essays. The Sand County Almanac was one of those university-assigned books that I could not part with and still have today. A must read if you are interesed in the mind of the Wisconsin borne man who set aside the first designated wilderness in New Mexico.</span>
                  
                    <div class="CustomerReviewSummary">A whole different world existing so near & yet so far.</div>
